      <p>I remember as a little girl being introduced by my Polish grandmother to sliced radishes which had been coated with a generous dollop of sour cream and sprinkled with salt.  While butter, salt and radishes are tasty, the tartness of sour cream tastes even better to me!  Try it!</p>
